      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Weiss</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Weiss_satellite_craters_map.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9d/Weiss_satellite_craters_map.jpg/330px-Weiss_satellite_craters_map.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"160\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9d/Weiss_satellite_craters_map.jpg/500px-Weiss_satellite_craters_map.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/9d/Weiss_satellite_craters_map.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Weiss_satellite_craters_map.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Weiss_(crater)\">Weiss</a> and its satellite craters  <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Weiss</b>, <br />\nan <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Terje_Kirstihagen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Terje Kirstihagen (page does not exist)\">Terje Kirstihagen</a>, \nwritten in <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a>, first released in November 2019 under the <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GPL 3</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\nWeiss was initially based on <a href=\"/Vice\" title=\"Vice\">Vice</a> and is inspired by <a href=\"/Ethereal\" title=\"Ethereal\">Ethereal</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a> and <a href=\"/Demolito\" title=\"Demolito\">Demolito</a>.\nIt is part of the <a href=\"/OpenBench\" title=\"OpenBench\">OpenBench</a> testing framework <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\nWeiss had its tournament debut at <a href=\"/TCEC_Season_18\" title=\"TCEC Season 18\">TCEC Season 18</a> in May 2020.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Features\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Features</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Board_Representation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Board Representation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Search\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Search</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Evaluation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Evaluation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Misc_2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Features\">Features</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Weiss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Features\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Board_Representation\"><a href=\"/Board_Representation\" title=\"Board Representation\">Board Representation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Weiss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Board Representation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Bitboard_Board-Definition#SixTwo\" title=\"Bitboard Board-Definition\">Dense Bitboard Board-Definition</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/8x8_Board\" title=\"8x8 Board\">8x8 Board</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards#Fancy\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Fancy Magic Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/BMI2#PEXTBitboards\" title=\"BMI2\">PEXT Bitboards</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Search\"><a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Weiss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Search\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Selectivity\" title=\"Selectivity\">Selectivity</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Check_Extensions\" title=\"Check Extensions\">Check Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mate_Distance_Pruning\" title=\"Mate Distance Pruning\">Mate Distance Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Reverse_Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Reverse Futility Pruning\">Reverse Futility Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning#MoveCountBasedPruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Late Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Razoring\" title=\"Razoring\">Razoring</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Delta_Pruning\" title=\"Delta Pruning\">Delta Pruning</a></li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Hash_Move\" title=\"Hash Move\">Hash Move</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Internal_Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Internal Iterative Deepening\">Internal Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/MVV-LVA\" title=\"MVV-LVA\">MVV/LVA</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Killer_Heuristic\" title=\"Killer Heuristic\">Killer Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">History Heuristic</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Evaluation\"><a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Weiss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Evaluation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Tapered_Eval\" title=\"Tapered Eval\">Tapered Eval</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bishop_Pair\" title=\"Bishop Pair\">Bishop Pair</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Piece-Square_Tables\" title=\"Piece-Square Tables\">Piece-Square Tables</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mobility\" title=\"Mobility\">Mobility</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Rook_on_Open_File\" title=\"Rook on Open File\">Rook on (Half) Open File</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Structure\" title=\"Pawn Structure\">Pawn Structure</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Passed Pawn\">Passed Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Isolated_Pawn\" title=\"Isolated Pawn\">Isolated Pawn</a></li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/King_Safety#VMOB\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety - Virtual Mobility</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tempo\" title=\"Tempo\">Tempo</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Weiss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a> using <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases#Fathom\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Fathom</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Perft\" title=\"Perft\">Perft</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Weiss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72369\">Engine release: weiss</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Terje_Kirstihagen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Terje Kirstihagen (page does not exist)\">Terje Kirstihagen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 19, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69754&amp;start=422\">Re: New engine releases 2019</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Terje_Kirstihagen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Terje Kirstihagen (page does not exist)\">Terje Kirstihagen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 06, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72613&amp;start=10\">Re: New engine releases 2020</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Terje_Kirstihagen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Terje Kirstihagen (page does not exist)\">Terje Kirstihagen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 07, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72613&amp;start=71\">Re: New engine releases 2020</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Terje_Kirstihagen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Terje Kirstihagen (page does not exist)\">Terje Kirstihagen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 14, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72613&amp;start=170\">Re: New engine releases 2020</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Terje_Kirstihagen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Terje Kirstihagen (page does not exist)\">Terje Kirstihagen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 25, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76209&amp;start=458\">Re: New engine releases &amp; news 2021</a> (Weiss 1.4) by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Terje_Kirstihagen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Terje Kirstihagen (page does not exist)\">Terje Kirstihagen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 02, 2021</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Weiss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Engine\">Chess Engine</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Weiss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Engine\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/TerjeKir/weiss\">GitHub - GitHub - TerjeKir/weiss: Weiss - a UCI chess engine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ccrl.chessdom.com/ccrl/4040/cgi/compare_engines.cgi?family=Weiss&amp;print=Rating+list&amp;print=Results+table&amp;print=LOS+table&amp;print=Ponder+hit+table&amp;print=Eval+difference+table&amp;print=Comopp+gamenum+table&amp;print=Overlap+table&amp;print=Score+with+common+opponents\">Weiss</a> in <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL 40/15</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc_2\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Weiss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/weiss\">weiss - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/Weiss\">Weiss - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/wei%C3%9F\">weiß - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/white\">white - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Weiss\">Weiss from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Weiss_(crater)\">Weiss (crater) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wei%C3%9F\">Weiß – Wikipedia.de</a> (German)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/White\">White from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://no.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hvit\">Hvit – Wikipedia.no</a> (Bokmål)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nn.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kvit\">Kvit – Wikipedia.nn</a> (Nynorsk)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.discogs.com/artist/1419247-H%C3%A4nsche-Weiss-Quintett\">Häns'che Weiss Quintett</a>, Dutch TV, 1977, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> Lineup: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/H%C3%A4ns%27che_Weiss\">Häns'che Weiss</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lulu_Reinhardt\">Lulu Reinhardt</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ziroli_Winterstein\">Ziroli Winterstein</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Titi_Winterstein\">Titi Winterstein</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.discogs.com/artist/1419244-Hojok-Merstein\">Hojok Merstein</a></dd>\n<dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/cdBYdFTbBIU?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Weiss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Weiss_(crater)\">Weiss</a> (named after Austrian astronomer <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edmund_Weiss\">Edmund Weiss</a>) and its satellite <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Impact_crater\">craters</a> on the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moon\">moon</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Weiss_satellite_craters_map.jpg\">Image</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:%D0%90%D0%BD%D0%B4%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%B9_%D0%A9%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B1%D0%B0%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B2\">Андрей Щербаков</a>, October 30, 2013, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Commons\">Wikimedia Commons</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72369\">Engine release: weiss</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Terje_Kirstihagen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Terje Kirstihagen (page does not exist)\">Terje Kirstihagen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 19, 2019</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a